text:
Marshland lies further ahead Raptor Nest Platform area.
A zig-zag boardwalk run across the Marshland waters where a bird nest-like design Shelter stood.
When it rains, rainwater from the upper Marshland flows to the lower Marshland. It then flows along Ficus Stream, cascade down Ficus Hill Stream and eventually into Alkaff Lake.
A bit wetland but is kinda wonderful experience
Nice place to walk in the morning or evening
